{"type": "article", "id": 26990, "title": "来，干了这杯牛奶，再吞下这个杯子", "description": "这个组合就是牛奶加饼干的肥沃口感。", "date": "2016-05-18T12:58:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27791, "name": "饼干杯"}, {"id": 27792, "name": "The Cookie Shot"}, {"id": 27793, "name": "the dirty cookie"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 289, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132740HWwrG3gVBRPesmzo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">著名的奥利奥饼干有一个洗脑广告：要把夹着白色奶油的黑色饼干沾着香喷喷的牛奶一起下咽，这个套路如此流畅，以至于“扭一扭、舔一舔、泡一泡”深入人心。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">现在，美国加州一个叫 The dirty cookie 的甜品店推出了一款让牛奶和饼干绑定在一起的甜食，还起了一个有趣的名字叫 The Cookie Shot。言外之意就是，你要像喝威士忌一样，仰头干了这一杯食物。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132734ke4dMaVc1QoBsjWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021327350ATMse1bOfNPWQGr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82107023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132735u6mOj4lFZWKp7wix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132736peOwxl5kFIyaQSgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132736tnROyLYaqXxd3U9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021327366tXuipsBLlGdH0rW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98657718\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132737zE1QiFGocna2LhjH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1459144\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132737yzPQLpjIUMEh6tAr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96806723\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132738nI6eiQDBrA2u9mG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90709459\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132738piFveXb3LVytj05a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91979522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">The Cookie Shot 的吃法分为几个步骤，首先需要选出你喜欢的饼干口味，目前有巧克力、巧克力和奶油，红丝绒，双倍巧克力，花色混合 5 种口味。店内还时不时推出抹茶、南瓜的饼干口味。第二步则需要选择牛奶的味道，有巧克力、香草和原味牛奶可供选择。最后一步，就可以开吃了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">“我们是一个年轻，富有创造力的团队。我们想要把饼干拉升到一个新高度。”<a href=\"http://thedirtycookieoc.com/about-us/\">The dirty cookie 的官网简介上写道</a>。同时，他们还自恋地说：“如果你把 The Cookie Shot 晒到社交网路上，相信一定会收到很多点赞。\"</p>\n<p class=\"\">的确，这些饼干加牛奶的食物做得小巧迷人。如果是预定版，还能在杯子上做一些蝙蝠侠、超人陆战队的大白的卡通形象。</p>\n<p class=\"\">“饼干的口感比较硬，味道比一般的饼干也更浓稠。“ <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BDWhE_SIZ9t/?taken-by=thedirtycookieoc\">食客 pineappledecay 在这家店铺的 Instagram 上评价。</a>这大概也是可以保证牛奶不渗出饼干的秘诀。</p>\n<p>The Cookie Shot  的单价售卖是 4.5 美元一个。除此之外，这家店铺也承办宴会或酒席。如果有人需要举办宴会，可以在官网上预订，12 个饼干售价 54 美元。<br></p>\n<p>作为一家甜品店，The dirty cookie 不只售卖让你一口闷的 The Cookie Shot，它还做了多味黄油饼干，根本没有饼干的形状，就是一大坨糊糊。有抹茶味、奥利奥奶油味、红丝绒味，吃法就是用华夫饼沾着吃。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132739qdWct56YKN0bEoHI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95869191\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132739nqyYZWwtMemNIS1u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96557659\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132740wk2oONn3BUTJZX76.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00510204\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">饼干黄油</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">作为一枚不想和自己过不去的正常人类，除了“啊好想试试”之外真的不知道还能说什么别的了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图均来自：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thedirtycookieoc/\">The dirty cookie @ Instagram</a> 、<a href=\"http://thedirtycookieoc.com/about-us/\">thedirtycookieoc.com</a>。</p>\n\n"}